Various notes about things and such

  - Big backgrounds can be very quickly filled in using:
    
    var fill = ctx.createPattern(image, 'repeat');
    ctx.fillStyle = fill;
    ctx.fillRect(0, 0, WIDTH, HEIGHT);

  - Hit map collision detection:
  
    1) Intersect character box with map hit map
    2) If anything in the character box then you have a hit